node.title: Russia's massive military buildup: Photos
node.description: Photos from Russia's borders show a recent amassing of weapons, vehicles and personnel.
node.content: ["Tension between Russia and its western neighbor, Ukraine, have escalated in recent months. Russia has\u00a0moved\u00a0troops and weaponry closer to Ukraine's borders, raising concern from the U.S. and its allies that President Vladimir Putin could order an invasion of the country.", "Even as Moscow has insisted it has no plans for an invasion, it has lodged a slew of warnings and complaints to Western leaders.", "Here's a look at Russia's current military capabilities, as observed from recent satellite photos as well as up-close photos of its military equipment and troops."]
